Package gpigb.report

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Reporter  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Reporter1
    Reports a Sensor that has a value out of range, it reports the Sensor, time and value.
    Reporter2
    A reporter which is designed to be used with Analyser2
    ReporterGUI
    Invokes an analyser from a reporter interface to provide analysis over the provided date range.
    ReporterPlotRTSmart
    A Real Time graph which can be used to plot sensor data
    SimpleWebReporter
    A reporter which presents a small web server to allow web viewing of system performance
    SmartGrapher
    The SmartGrapher provides a view of three populations of values (the current integer value, the overall average and the moving average) as a line graph over time.
